libcork includes implementations of a number of useful data structures.

  • Resizable arrays
  • Bit sets
  • Binary slices
  • Managed binary buffers
  • Resizable binary buffers
  • Stream processing
  • Doubly-linked lists
  • Hash tables
  • Ring buffers
